form_title.ms_form_title_llm_v1: CERTIFICATION ON ALIEN'S FIRSTNAME CHANGE AND CO-JOINING LASTNAME, 39/2516

full_text: Screened by NARA, 9/27/2023 ROYAL EMBLEM A CERTIFICATION ON ALIEN'S FIRSTNAME CHANGE AND CO-JOINING LASTNAME A.C. SERVICE LIMITED PARTNERSHIP No. 39/2516 This document is given to show that Mr. Yee Chong Sae Lao, Chinese Nationality, has submitted an application to change Firstname to 11 Charoen " and to co-joining Lastname as " Charukijphitthayakul ". The local Registrar has received such application, and the matter is under an approval consideration. This certificate is issued on 6th day of March 1973 - Signature - (Mr. Prasit Taweeto) Second District Officer, acting for the local Registrar of Bang Rak District, Bangkok Metropolis. OFFICIAL SEAL AFFIXED District Administration Office. Tel: 30611 CERTIFIED CORRECT TRANSLATION PER DOCOMENT tim SERI THAMPICHA MANAGER 20 MAY 1987
